org.baswell.easybeans

Annotation Type EasyBeanDescriptor


  • @Target(value={TYPE,CONSTRUCTOR,METHOD,FIELD})
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface EasyBeanDescriptor
    Descriptor information for classes, constructors, methods or fields. The number of names should matches the number of values.
